# Forge Kit RAG Configuration
# Set the comma-separated list of repository paths to index for RAG
# Format: path1,path2,path3
# Paths can be absolute or relative to HOME (e.g. ~/Desenvolvimento/my-repo)
#
# Example:
# RAG_REPOS=/path/to/repo1,~/Desenvolvimento/repo2,/absolute/path/repo3
#
# If this file is not present, set the RAG_REPOS environment variable instead:
# export RAG_REPOS="/path/to/repo1,/path/to/repo2"
#
# If neither is configured, the RAG indexer will skip code sources with a warning.

RAG_REPOS=
